# 🧠 AI System Design Interviewer — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A production-grade, multi-agent GenAI platform for adaptive system design interview simulation. The system spans **3 services**, **60+ files**, and implements real GenAI patterns (MCP, A2A, RAG).

