## Components Built

### Spring Boot API Gateway (28 files)

| Layer | Files | Purpose |
|-------|-------|---------|
| Controllers | `InterviewController`, `HealthController` | REST API + A2A discovery |
| Services | `InterviewService`, `SessionService` | Business logic, Redis session management |
| Agents | `InterviewAgent`, `QuestionAgent`, `EvaluationAgent`, `HintAgent` | A2A multi-agent orchestration |
| Models | 3 entities, 7 DTOs, 3 enums | Domain model with adaptive difficulty |
| Config | `RedisConfig`, `CorsConfig`, `WebSocketConfig`, `AppConfig` | Infrastructure configuration |
| Client | `LlmServiceClient` | HTTP client to Python MCP service |

### Python LLM Service (15 files)

| Module | Files | Purpose |
|--------|-------|---------|
| Tools | `rag_tool`, `scoring_tool`, `diagram_tool`, `hint_tool` | MCP tool implementations |
| LLM | `gemini_client`, `prompts` | Gemini API wrapper + prompt templates |
| RAG | `embeddings`, `retriever`, `indexer` | Pinecone vector search pipeline |
| Router | `mcp_tools` | MCP-compatible endpoints with manifest |

### React Frontend (8 files)

| Page | Key Features |
|------|-------------|
| Landing | Hero section, 3 company modes, 10 topics grid, animated selection |
| Interview | Split-pane layout, chat thread, live scoring sidebar, progressive hints |
| Results | Animated radial charts, rubric breakdown, round-by-round review, architecture diagram |

### Knowledge Base (10 documents)

- **Patterns**: Caching, Sharding, Load Balancing, CAP Theorem, Message Queues, Database Design, Microservices
- **Architectures**: URL Shortener, Netflix, Uber

