## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| LLM Provider | Google Gemini (free tier) | Cost-free for portfolio, `response_mime_type` for structured JSON |
| Database | Supabase PostgreSQL | Persistent production-ready storage for interview sessions |
| A2A Protocol | Lightweight custom pattern | Official SDK still maturing, custom gives full control |
| RAG Fallback | Hardcoded knowledge map | Ensures system works even without Pinecone index built |
| Adaptive Difficulty | Score-based adjustment | `score >= 8` → harder, `score <= 4` → easier |
| Company Modes | Weighted rubrics | Google emphasizes scalability (2.5x), Amazon emphasizes trade-offs (2.5x) |

